<p>ItŌĆÖs not always clear whether a personŌĆÖs words are actually announcing a disaster. <a href="https://storage.googleapis.com/kaggle-media/competitions/tweet_screenshot.png">This tweet</a> explicitly uses the word ŌĆ£ABLAZEŌĆØ but means it metaphorically. This is clear to a human right away, especially with the visual aid. But itŌĆÖs less clear to a machine.<br />
